{"tid":589792,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲睇過《隔世救未來/黑洞頻率》？","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T04:17:49.000Z","uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"42490f52419dff61857524dfd60b00ad09f128e6","tid":589792,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/133315_387376f4a8444c11ff89006f99f782f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F133315_387376f4a8444c11ff89006f99f782f7.png&h=ee409a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n套戲講部無線電機可以接通「過去」同「現在」，主角係兩父子，30年前個老豆因為救火燒死咗，有一晚，阿仔用部無線電聯絡上30年前未死嘅老豆，點知真係改變歷史，救返老豆但護士老母被人先女女女後殺，跟住兩父子隔空查案，要改變歷史.....<br />\n<br />\n覺得幾刺激，有冇巴絲睇過？<br />\n<br />\n有時部手機有（無來電顯示）嘅電話打黎....都會諗起我老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e980fd35f06664f4964439c29714d16ea657ee85","tid":589792,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"即係隔世追兇抄佢?"},{"pid":"cd1dca4828afb836d11d48fa2f2b4c9962feaf64","tid":589792,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n香港叫隔世追兇吖嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c1c7e8f85042735f7a7c5da4676d6dfcbdbafa","tid":589792,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好話抄<br />\n咁個提材咁好,唔借黎拍咪會曬晒<br />\n其實CCTVB咪大方D 話明借鏡咪得囉~~我唔信鬼佬會告佢<br />\n比人發現左,又唔寫明參考,咪比人感覺唔好"},{"pid":"23ee2e93b688dba26bc232f56f036eaac385ffa4","tid":589792,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbea597daf2081e84c80f4c65a7f483409a5f85","tid":589792,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:31:22.000Z"